{"title":"太阳","authors":["梁谢成"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":1,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁谢成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的嘴巴光光的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光光的嘴巴没有胡须"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的面庞圆圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆圆的面庞没有皱纹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的眼神亮亮的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮亮的眼神不怕黑暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的心肠热热的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热热的心肠不怕严寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，在你面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑暗逃遁了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严寒退却了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光明与温暖，青春与欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐翩翩起舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在蓬勃向上的旋律中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋转着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去　现在　未来"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}